'''Peacekeepers''' were the law enforcement agency of the [[Outbound Flight Colony]]. They were led by the [[Guardian of the People]] and obeyed the orders of the [[Director/Legends|Director]] and the [[Managing Council]]. Every resident took a term as a Peacekeeper.<ref name="SQ">''[[Survivor's Quest]]''</ref>

In [[22 ABY/Legends|22 ABY]] the Guardian was [[Jorad Pressor]]. The ten other Peacekeepers included [[Trilli]], [[Oliet]], [[Ronson]], [[Bels]], [[Amberson]], [[Perry]], and [[Quinze]]. Six were killed by the [[Vagaari/Legends|Vagaari]] in the [[Battle of the Redoubt]].<ref name="SQ" />

